Table 1. The top-1 classification accuracy on ImageNet-1K, object detection AP-box on COCO with Cascade Mask R-CNN, and semantic 
segmentation mIoU on ADE20K with UperNet of dBOT using different models as the initialized teacher network. Note that all models 
are pre-trained on ImageNet-1K, including DALL-E, for a fair comparison. We perform distillation in each stage for 800 epochs. In the 
1 st stage, we distill from initialized teacher to obtain a student. In the subsequent (i.e., 2 nd , 3 rd , etc.) stages, the obtained students are 
leveraged as bootstrapped teacher to distill a new student.
